song.title: Abyss Game 2 (Emulate the Past mix)
song.info:
Lyrics:
This one is for all of those people who still want more, of all the great tunes sung by the Commodore. And feel the world is moving just a tad too fast.
We feel nostalgic about these songs because it reminds us of a time that we have lost. and now we're keeping it alive while having a blast.
Emulating the past.
